      "writtenOn": "2016-05-06T20:55:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "this all is a little heavyweight what about a union of void* and CRITICAL_SECTION just inside of the class body, so it\u0027s allocated statically?\nAlso",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 130,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 134,
        "endChar": 54
      },
      "revId": "4be426ccd2fa932602c136b3cc5244282b684d17",
